  "title": "Three people reported a flash light flying 150 ft above their heads in Curitiba-PR [1995]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/30/three-people-reported-a-flash-light-flying-150-ft-above-their-heads-in-curitiba-pr-1995/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1js",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 2nd, 1995</strong>. Time: 21h55. Duration: 3 seconds. Three people in the Bacacheri region, in Curitiba, State of Paraná, observed &#8220;a flash&#8221; about 50 meters above them. According to the description given by the witness, the object had no defined shape or size. The witness was only able to inform that the flash of light passed over them in a straight path towards the west. According to the report, the sky was clear and starry when the sighting took place in that region.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.394. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Bacacheri, Curitiba, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
